    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! Thanks for stopping by to check out my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it really shows\u2014she still has that incredible showroom shine and that fresh interior feel. It\u2019s been strictly garage-kept and treated with nothing but the best care; honestly, she purrs so smoothly you\u2019ll forget the engine is even running! There might be a tiny, barely-visible mark from a stray pebble on a Sunday drive, but you\u2019d honestly need a magnifying glass to find it. I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will love her just as much as I have. Come on by, let's grab a coffee and I'll show you around!",
